<para style="q1">

<verse number="13" style="v" />My God, make them like the whirling dust,</para>

<para style="q1">like chaff before the wind,</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="14" style="v" />like the fire that burns the forest,</para>

<para style="q1">and like the flame that sets the mountains on fire.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="15" style="v" />Chase them with your strong wind,</para>

<para style="q1">and terrify them with your windstorm.</para>
